{"type": "article", "id": 24003, "title": "可加高的圆木桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122622GOnN5rM4d1yvuzqi.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">圆桌对于小空间来说往往是奢侈，这个木制圆桌则将桌腿和桌面分开。除此之外，设计师还在三根桌腿上增加了一个小的模块，可以向积木一样拼在上面以增加高度，适应不同大小的房间。设计者 David Ciernicki 来自德国，这是之前桌子的升级版，开发圆形木桌的灵活和实用。<a href=\"http://davidciernicki.com/2016/02/01/major-tom-2-0/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122620syetaAuDVJizF8lo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122621QXPt9micCFdz75Jq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122621VEdl8spk1qhTeF0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 281px; width: 375px; left: 593px; top: 887px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060712262241w0SQpjlVeFxRUd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n\n\n"}